	1. Install Github from Intellij marketplace
	2. Go to intellij settings>Version Control>
	3. Navigate to Git
	4. Update the "Path to Git executable" where git is installed in your local machine. e.g. D:\ProgramFiles\Git\bin\git.exe
	5. In the GitHub sub-directory, add your github account.
	6. Go to Git tab and clone the repositories, by giving the git url and the directory in the below fields:
	->URL : https://github.com/debshankarghose/JavaExamples
	->Directory: D:\eclipse-workspace
